ATTRIBUTION:

Core persona vector extraction logic (core/generate_vec.py, core/activation_steer.py,
core/judge.py) adapted from https://github.com/safety-research/persona_vectors

All per-token monitoring (pertoken/), temporal analysis, and new trait definitions
(paternalism, deception, manipulativeness, corrigibility) are original contributions
by the authors of this repository.
